propel.core.collections.lists
Class SharedList<T>

java.lang.Object
  propel.core.collections.lists.ReifiedArrayList<T>
      propel.core.collections.lists.SharedList<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<T>, java.util.Collection<T>, java.util.List<T>, ISharedList<T>, ReifiedList<T>, ReifiedIterable<T>, IShared
public class SharedList<T>
extends ReifiedArrayList<T>
implements ISharedList<T>

An type-aware array-backed thread-safe list. This collection allows nulls to be inserted. Instantiate using e.g.: new SharedList<String>(){}; -OR- new SharedList<String>(String.class);
